{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Embark on the most absurd spacewalk of your life as a crew up to 8 unlucky souls, drifting through the chaotic void of space.    </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>    Explore  asteroid biomes and scavenge to pay your debt</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scavenge space to collect debris with the grab and throw feature, and pay your debt to the Galactic Confederation. You'll be able to discover up to 20 levels including special event missions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/Mad_Void_Debris.gif?t=1734527950\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cooperate\u2026 Or not</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can go outside by yourself, but you'll survive longer if find up to 7 other crew members and coordinate yourselves with proximity chat. Or you can just throw them on aliens, it's good fun too.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/GC_scrapper_4_people.gif?t=1734527950\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fast play sessions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You only have 5 minutes to bring enough debris and repay the Galactic Confederation. Make sure your time is not shorted by excruciating death! Use your jetpack to explore these places and avoid their dangers. </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/Mad_Void_Danger.gif?t=1734527950\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>    Upgrade your equipement to explore riskier zones</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Better jetpack, emergency kit, teleporter\u2026 Spend your supplies at the Scrapper HQ to prepare your crew. The more you succeed in missions, the more you\u2019ll be able to spend and explore very hostile 